title: Girls Soccer Roundup: Mansfield Christian and Crestview win
text:
Girls Soccer Roundup: Mansfield Christian and Crestview win Staff report 10:54 p.m. EDT October 20, 2015 STK Stock 3 CONNECT 1 TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Division III Sectional 
Mansfield Christian 7, Ada 0 
The Flames blanked Ada in Division III Sectional on Tuesday. Ashtyn Patrick had a hat trick plus one assist to lead Mansfield Christian. Elizabeth Sparks, Sara Johnson, Addalyn Patrick and Audrey Martin all had one goal apiece. Addalyn Patrick and Sparks also had one assist each. Taleah Favors had one save in goal to preserve the shutout. 
Crestview 4, St. Peter’s 1 
Crestview defeated St. Peter’s in Division III Sectional semi-final on Tuesday to advanced to the Sectional final against Allen East on Saturday. Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1RV12ad MORE STORIES
